GraphData.Name: 4 SC31 Request Welding on Position Reached and time passed
GraphData.Kommentar: Evaluate if time has passed (01 Wait time for welding) and if the scanner has reached the requested position (from the Move Scanner module). By default the welding starts when both conditions are met, to start when either condition is met set "Condition To Request Weld?" to OR
